\[0<\eta\leq\frac{1-\sigma^{2}}{L(1+\sigma^{2})}\text{ and }\rho=\frac{1-\sqrt{ \mu\eta}}{1+\sqrt{\mu\eta}},\text{ then }\mathbb{E}[f(x_{n})-f(x^{*})]\leq 2(1-\sqrt{\mu\eta})^{n} \,\mathbb{E}\left[f(x_{0})-f(x^{*})\right].\]

